    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "The boulder is beautifully situated beside the path on the way to the roped climbing at Runsa. Good rock, excellent landings and a pleasant height. A fine evening could be spent climbing the problems on Runsastenen, perhaps followed by some traversing on the wall about 150m further along the path on the right.",
