            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "The boulder is beautifully situated beside the path to the Runsa roped climbing. Good rock quality, excellent landings and a pleasant height. A fine evening can be spent climbing the problems on Runsastenen, perhaps followed by some traversing on the wall about 150 m further along the path on the right.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:runsastenen"
